    "closed_at": null,
    "body": "It seems npm features this weakness\r\n[CWE-494: Download of Code Without Integrity Check](http://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/494.html)\r\n\r\nnpm packages downloaded from the internet are not verified for integrity in any way.\r\nThis seems like a major security risk.\r\n\r\nThis has been discussed in several other issues and it is acknowledged as a deficiency but there seem to be no plans to address it.\r\n\r\nAt least npm should inform its users of this risk and make it clear that users should handle it on their own."
